rivate-aircraft-crashes-in-dominican-republic/articleshow/131576969.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T08:26:01+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131577058,imgsize-11304568.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Missiles rain across Israel's night sky as Iran launches fresh attacks after two months]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131576305.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iran launched missiles at Israel, triggering air raid sirens and forcing millions to shelters. Israel claims to have intercepted the projectiles, but explosions were heard. Tehran warned of broader retaliation after an earlier Israeli strike. Meanwhile, former US President Trump urged restraint, reportedly persuading Prime Minister Netanyahu to hold off on immediate response.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/watch-missiles-rain-across-israels-night-sky-as-iran-launches-fresh-attacks-after-two-months/articleshow/131576305.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/watch-missiles-rain-across-israels-night-sky-as-iran-launches-fresh-attacks-after-two-months/articleshow/131576305.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-08T07:17:08+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131576321,imgsize-12634140.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Buildings turn to rubble after powerful 8.1 earthquake hits Philippines]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131576251.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A powerful 8.1-magnitude earthquake struck the Philippines, causing 